<H2 SUBJECT='The HIGZ graphics editor'>The HIGZ graphics editor
<I1>graphics editor
<I1>editor
<I1>PICTURE/MODIFY
<P>The HIGZ pictures in memory could be modified interactively with the HIGZ
graphics editor. The command:
<XMP>
PAW > <HP3>PICT/MODIFY PNAME</HP3>
</XMP>
invokes the graphics editor. PNAME could be the complete name, the picture number in memory or ' '.
<P>The following figure (produced by the graphics editor itself) gives more
details on the graphics editor's functionality.
